      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S MAX (6) finished midfield on debut (19.32) then better for the experience broke through last time to score a neck maiden win (19.38) at Q Straight. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Looks the testing material. MISS MULGOWIE (2) was a little disappointing last start at this track when 7th (26.14) over 457m. Has never missed the frame here at the trip including one win. Shapes as one to consider. SHINE ON ANNIE (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (26.08) in a Grade 6 at this track. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Should be about the money. TRAVELLING DEAN (8) collected a minor prize last start out of the same box - must be considered.",
